#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Features</title>"
msgstr "<title>Característiques</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: features.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Features</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Característiques</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important features and improvements are highlighted here, it would "
"make this list too long if we were to include <emphasis>all</emphasis> the "
"features and improvements. You will discover even more features in this "
"documentation and in the <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?"
"path=ChangeLog\"><filename>ChangeLog</filename></ulink> and <ulink url="
"\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS\"><filename>NEWS</filename></"
"ulink> files."
msgstr ""
"Aquí es ressalten les característiques i millores més importants, aquesta "
"llista seria massa llarga si haguéssim d'incloure <emphasis>totes</emphasis> "
"les característiques i millores. En aquesta documentació encara descobrireu "
"més característiques així com als fitxers <ulink url=\"https://commits.kde."
"org/krusader?path=ChangeLog\"><filename>Changelog</filename></ulink> i "
"<ulink url=\"https://commits.kde.org/krusader?path=NEWS\"><filename>NEWS</"
"filename></ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml\">Orthodox File "
"Manager (OFM)</ulink> features"
msgstr ""
"Característiques <ulink url=\"http://www.softpanorama.org/OFM/index.shtml"
"\">del gestor de fitxers ortodox (OFM)</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Two powerful and easy to use <link linkend=\"panels\">OFM panels</link>."
msgstr ""
"Dos <link linkend=\"panels\">plafons OFM</link> potents i fàcils d'emprar."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"cmdline\">Command Line</link> and optional <link linkend="
"\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> below."
msgstr ""
"A la part inferior hi ha una <link linkend=\"cmdline\">línia d'ordres</link> "
"i un <link linkend=\"termemu\">emulador de terminal</link> opcional."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Strong <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">keyboard</link> orientation and "
"the ability to perform all functions without the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Una forta orientació al <link linkend=\"keyboard-commands\">teclat</link> i "
"la capacitat de realitzar totes les funcions sense el ratolí."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context-dependent invocation of scripts and programs &eg; mouse click/"
"&Enter; (execute or open with the associated application), <keycap>F3</"
"keycap> (view) and <keycap>F4</keycap> (edit)."
msgstr ""
"La invocació dependrà del context dels scripts i programes, &pex;, fer clic "
"del ratolí/prémer la tecla &Intro; (executa o obre amb l'aplicació "
"associada), <keycap>F3</keycap> (visualitza) i <keycap>F4</keycap> (edita)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">User Menu</link>, create your own customized "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">Menú d'usuari</link>, creeu el vostre propi "
"menú personalitzat."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"History &eg; <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Folder History</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"popular-urls\">Popular &URL;s</link>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Historial, &pex;, <link linkend=\"folderhistory\">Historial de carpetes</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"popular-urls\">Els &URL; populars</link>, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file systems (VFS)</link> &eg; for <link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>, <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>, search results, synchronizer."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"vfs\">Sistemes de fitxers virtuals (VFS)</link>, &pex;, per "
"a <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">connexions remotes</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"archives\">arxius</link>, resultat de la cerca, sincronitzador."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Powerful internal <link linkend=\"krviewer\">viewer and editor</link> via "
"kparts supporting almost every file format."
msgstr ""
"Un potent <link linkend=\"krviewer\">visualitzador i editor</link> intern "
"mitjançant les KParts que admet gairebé tots els formats de fitxer."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Advanced Search module</link>: searching in "
"archives and search content on remote file systems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Mòdul de cerca avançada</link>: cerca als "
"arxius i cerca per contingut en els sistemes de fitxers remots."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several Panel view modes via the <link linkend=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</link>."
msgstr ""
"Diversos modes de vista del plafó a través de la <link linkend=\"sidebar"
"\">barra lateral</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; tools"
msgstr "Eines del &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote Connections</link>: &FTP;/SAMBA "
"with SFTP/SCP support via KIO Slaves"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Connexions remotes</link>: &FTP;/SAMBA "
"amb suport SFTP/SCP mitjançant els esclaus KIO"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"locate\">Locate</link> &GUI; frontend"
msgstr "Frontal de la &IGU; del «<link linkend=\"locate\">locate</link>»"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize Folders"
msgstr "Sincronitza les carpetes"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount-Manager"
msgstr "Gestor de muntatge"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk Usage"
msgstr "Ús del disc"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Root mode"
msgstr "Mode administrador"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; features"
msgstr "Característiques del &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Archive Handling: browsing, unpack, pack, testing. Supported <link linkend="
"\"archives\">archives</link>: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, rar, "
"rpm, tar, zip and 7-zip."
msgstr ""
"Maneig dels arxius: navegació, desempaquetat, empaquetat, prova. <link "
"linkend=\"archives\">Arxius</link> admesos: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, "
"lha, rar, rpm, tar, zip i 7-zip."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Checksum Creation and Verification</link> "
"mechanism that supports md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, sha512, "
"tiger, whirlpool, cfv, and crc."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"checksum\">Mecanisme de creació i verificació de la suma de "
"verificació</link>, el qual admet md5, sha1, sha256, sha224, sha256, sha384, "
"sha512, tiger, whirlpool, cfv i crc."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calculate occupied space</link> of files and "
"folders, archives and remote filesystems."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calcula l'espai ocupat</link> pels fitxers i "
"carpetes, arxius i sistemes de fitxers remots."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Directory comparison</link> and <link linkend="
"\"view-menu\">filtering</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Comparació</link> i <link linkend=\"view-menu"
"\">filtratge</link> de la carpeta."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Compare files by content</link> via "
"external diff programs like &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> "
"or <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</"
"application></ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"compare-content\">Compara els fitxers per contingut</link> "
"mitjançant programes externs de diff com el &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink> o <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Rename</link> files and folders via <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/krename/"
"\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"multi_rename\">Canvia el nom</link> dels fitxers i carpetes "
"mitjançant el <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/utilities/"
"krename/\"><application>KRename</application></ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Completely supports drag'n'drop: drag from &konqueror; straight into a "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> file, from &krusader;'s panel "
"into the trash bin, the desktop or into &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Admet totalment arrossegar i deixar anar: s'arrossega directament des del "
"&konqueror; cap a un fitxer <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>, "
"des del plafó del &krusader; cap a dins de la paperera, de l'escriptori o "
"cap al &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Preserve date</link> for local targets at "
"copy/move operations."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-advanced\">Conserva la data</link> per a les "
"destinacions locals en les operacions de copiar/moure."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> opens a <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">Terminal Window</"
"link> in the current folder."
msgstr ""
"<keycap>F9</keycap> obre una <link linkend=\"tools-menu\">finestra de "
"terminal</link> en la carpeta actual."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Easy editing of <link linkend=\"file-menu\">file permissions</link> and "
"ownership and <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view\">Numeric Permissions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Edita amb facilitat els <link linkend=\"file-menu\">permisos i propietat "
"dels fitxers</link>, així com els <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-view"
"\">permisos numèrics</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Selection filters</link> used in &eg; "
"Synchronizer and KruSearcher."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"krusearcher\">Selecciona els filtres</link> emprats en "
"&pex;, el Sincronitzador i el KruSearcher."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jump-Back"
msgstr "Torna a un punt de retorn"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"konfig-general\"> &MIME; type-aware</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Reconeixement del tipus &MIME;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Tabbed panels</link> and <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Tabbed Editor/Viewer</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Plafons en pestanyes</link> i <link linkend="
"\"krviewer\">Editor/Visualitzador en pestanyes</link>."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick search, select and filter"
msgstr "Cerca ràpida, selecciona i filtra"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "File splitter"
msgstr "Divisor del fitxer"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Gestures"
msgstr "Gestos del ratolí"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Quick Navigation</link> in the Location Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Navegació ràpida</link> a la Barra d'eines de "
"localització."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "WhatsThis Help function in favour of tooltips where reasonable."
msgstr ""
"La funció d'ajuda «Què és això?» a favor dels consells d'eina quan aquesta "
"és raonable."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sync-browsing"
msgstr "Navegació sincronitzada"

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customize &krusader; to your own needs"
msgstr "Personalitzeu el &krusader; a les vostres necessitats"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\"> Konfigurator</link> &krusader;'s "
"configuration center."
msgstr ""
"El <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Konfigurador</link> és el centre de "
"configuració del &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main Toolbar</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</link> for user actions and bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Barra d'eines principal</link>, <link linkend="
"\"actions_toolbar\">Barra d'eines d'accions</link> per a les accions "
"d'usuari i les adreces d'interès."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-bindings"
msgstr "Lligams de tecla"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Colors"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel profiles"
msgstr "Perfils del plafó"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark-Manager"
msgstr "Gestor d'adreces d'interès"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selection Modes"
msgstr "Modes de selecció"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many more features can be <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">configured</link> "
"the way you like."
msgstr ""
"Es poden <link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">configurar</link> moltes més "
"característiques de la manera que més us agradi."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; Extensions"
msgstr "Extensions del &krusader;"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "UserActions"
msgstr "Accions d'usuari"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Profiles"
msgstr "Perfils de color"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key-binding Profiles"
msgstr "Perfils dels lligams de tecla"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Download and upload your favourite &krusader; extensions at <ulink url="
"\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Baixeu i pugeu les vostres extensions preferides del &krusader; a la <ulink "
"url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: features.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"New features in the &krusader;-1.80.0 <quote>Final 3rd Stone</quote> release"
msgstr ""
"Característiques noves amb el llançament del &krusader; 1.80.0 «Final 3rd "
"Stone»"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Archive improvements"
msgstr "Millores amb els arxius"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Password support</link> for: arj, ace, rar and "
"zip. Passwords can be stored in <application>Kwallet</application>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Admet les contrasenyes</link> per a: arj, ace, "
"rar i zip. Les contrasenyes es poden emmagatzemar a la <application>Kwallet</"
"application>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">7-zip support</link>, by external applications "
"<application>7z</application> and <application>7za</application>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Admet 7-zip</link>, per a les aplicacions "
"externes <application>7z</application> i <application>7za</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Auto-detection support</link>, allowing you to "
"open <quote>hidden archives</quote> (&eg; <trademark class=\"registered"
"\">OpenOffice</trademark> documents)."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"archives\">Admet la detecció automàtica</link>, el qual "
"permet obrir els «arxius ocults» (&pex;, documents de l'<trademark class="
"\"registered\">OpenOffice</trademark>)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packing/unpacking is now in the background."
msgstr "Ara, el fet d'empaquetar/desempaquetar resta en segon pla."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brief View"
msgstr "Vista breu"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many improvements of the <link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> "
"system."
msgstr ""
"Moltes millores en el sistema <link linkend=\"useractions\">Accions "
"d'usuari</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Countless usability enhancements, especially in Konfigurator and the heavily "
"reordered menubar."
msgstr ""
"Innumerables millores en la usabilitat, especialment en el Konfigurador i la "
"barra de menús, la qual s'ha tornat a ordenar."

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Media button"
msgstr "Botó Suports"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy/Move: <link linkend=\"copying\">preserve all attributes</link> (time, "
"owner, group)."
msgstr ""
"Copiar/Moure: <link linkend=\"copying\">conserva tots els atributs</link> "
"(temps, propietari, grup)."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Dim the colors of the inactive panel</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Ajusta els colors del plafó inactiu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Renaming a filename without extension, single instance mode, start to system "
"tray, check this out in <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator</link>"
msgstr ""
"Canvia el nom d'un nom de fitxer sense extensió, mode instància única, "
"inicia a la safata del sistema, marqueu-ho al <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfigurador</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configurable <link linkend=\"list_panel\">Atomic extensions</link>, so that "
"extensions like <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> are shown as "
"one part in the <guilabel>Ext Column</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"list_panel\">Extensions atòmiques</link> configurables, de "
"manera que les extensions com <literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> "
"es mostraran com una part a la columna <guilabel>Ext</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for bookmarks and enable/disable special bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Menú contextual per a les adreces d'interès i habilitar/inhabilitar les "
"adreces d'interès especials."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restyled <link linkend=\"menu-commands\">MenuBar</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"menu-commands\">Barra de menús</link> redissenyada"

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> enhancements bringing new "
"functions, new usages and new look."
msgstr ""
"Millores a l'<link linkend=\"termemu\">emulador de terminal</link> que "
"aporten noves funcions, nous usos i una nova aparença."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronizer</link> enhancements and parallel "
"threads for slow &FTP; servers."
msgstr ""
"Millores del <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">sincronitzador</link> i els fils "
"en paral·lel per als servidors d'&FTP; lents."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Single instance mode</link>, <link linkend="
"\"konfig-startup\">start to system tray</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"konfig-startup\">Mode d'instància única</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"konfig-startup\">s'inicia a la safata del sistema</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: features.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menu for permanent bookmarks."
msgstr "Menú contextual per a les adreces d'interès permanents."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full support for <link linkend=\"acl\">ACL permissions</link>, like "
"properties, preserve attributes, synchronizer and other."
msgstr ""
"Suport complet per als <link linkend=\"acl\">permisos ACL</link>, com les "
"propietats, conserva els atributs, sincronitzador i altres."

#. Tag: para
#: features.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
